message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This exceptional item has been meticulously crafted and holds significant value to us, which we believe is well above $8,000. Given its quality and uniqueness, we're offering it to you at a special price tailored to your expectations. Considering its worth to you, we propose a price of $9,500. This offer allows you to acquire an item that could potentially be worth much more in the future, while also securing a valuable asset at a competitive rate. We look forward to your consideration.
